вЂў `glow -p file.md` вЂ” open in pager (scrollable, press q to quit)
вЂў `glow .` вЂ” browse all markdown files in the current directory (TUI)
вЂў `glow https://...` вЂ” render a remote URL (if network available)
вЂў Works well with READMEs, changelogs, docs

(press q to return)
EOF

	echo
	hdr "Try it:"
	local sl; sl=$(skill_level)
	case "$sl" in
		beginner)
